            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">52.209-2</ph> Prohibition on Contracting with Inverted Domestic Corporations-Representation.</title>
		    <conbody outputclass="provision" class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <p id="d3107e13" class="- topic/p ">As prescribed in <ph class="- topic/ph ">
					          <xref href="FAR-i1116431.dita#i1116431"
                     base="i1116431"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">9.108-5</xref>(a)</ph>, insert the following provision:</p>
			      <p outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" class="- topic/p ">Prohibition on Contracting with Inverted Domestic Corporations-Representation (Nov 2015)</p>
			      <ol id="d3089e25" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d3107e29" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            
						            <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Definitions</i>. “Inverted domestic corporation” and “subsidiary” have the meaning given in the clause of this contract entitled Prohibition on Contracting with Inverted Domestic Corporations (<xref href="FAR-i1062680.dita#i1062680"
                        base="i1062680"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.209-10</xref>).</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d3107e44" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Government agencies are not permitted to use appropriated (or otherwise made available) funds for contracts with either an inverted domestic corporation, or a subsidiary of an inverted domestic corporation, unless the exception at <xref href="FAR-i1116407.dita#i1116407"
                        base="i1116407"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">9.108-2</xref>(b) applies or the requirement is waived in accordance with the procedures at <xref href="FAR-i1116422.dita#i1116422"
                        base="i1116422"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">9.108-4</xref>.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d3107e59" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            
						            <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Representation</i>. The Offeror represents that-</p>
					          <ol id="d3089e68" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d3107e72" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                It □is, □is not an inverted domestic corporation; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d3107e81" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                It □is, □is not a subsidiary of an inverted domestic corporation.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
			      <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Endofprovision">(End of provision)</p>
